quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  114,1,"Tharowangka: A Mulindong Ako ko Kadnan o manga Manosiya"
  114,2,A Phapa-ar ko manga Manosiya
  114,3,A Tohan o manga Manosiya
  114,4,"Po-on ko karata-an o Puphangonsi, a Puphano-o so-ok"
  114,5,So Puphangonsi ko manga rarub o manga Manosiya
  114,6,"A pud ko manga Jinn, a go so manga Manosiya"